summary: The contact owns a 2021 East to West Silver Lake RV. The contact stated that the refrigerator was inoperable. There was no warning light illuminated. The contact had food waste due to spoilage. The vehicle was taken to the local dealer to be diagnosed. The contact was informed that the refrigerator needed to be replaced. The vehicle was not repaired. The manufacturer was not contacted. The failure mileage was unknown. The VIN was not available.
